This paper is primarily focused on enhancing the privacy of web search, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses the use of search queries and the design of a browser extension, which involves information retrieval (cs.IR) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of cookies and the prevention of information leakage, which are related to database systems (cs.DB) and social and information networks (cs.SI).
